response.original_title: Figure Skating Superstars: Katarina Witt and Friends
response.overview: Uninhibited by competitive scoring, figure skating's most talented athletes are free to execute some of the most daring, innovative and technically challenging moves on ice. This one-of-a-kind lineup features breathtaking routines by Katarina Witt, Viktor Petrenko, the Duchesnays, Christopher Bowman, Tonya Harding and others. Bonus features include a biography of Olympic gold medalist Witt, 11 skater profiles and much more.
response.title: Figure Skating Superstars: Katarina Witt and Friends
